episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: 1988. On the night of their graduation, Emma and Dexter meet for the first time. It's an evening of almost-romance, and a morning of missed opportunity.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: 1989. The year has taken Dex and Em in very different directions. From a villa in Rome and a minibus in the Midlands, they both ponder what comes next.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: 1990. Life in London isn't what Em was expecting. In a creative drought, she's working in a shabby restaurant, where she gets a visit from Dex.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: 1991. On holiday together in Greece, Emma has plans for how to keep things platonic. Dexter would rather reminisce about the night they met.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: 1992. After a heavy night out, a hungover Dexter goes home to visit his family. Shocked at the terrible state he's in, his mother takes him to task.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: 1993. Dex gets his moment in the spotlight, while it's opening night for Em's play. She boosts her actors' confidence, while he suffers a dent to his.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: 1994. The friends go for a glamorous but disastrous dinner together. Dexter's keen to show off his lavish new lifestyle, but Emma isn't impressed.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: 1995. On the last day of the school term, Emma gets into a compromising position at work. When she gets home, things become even more uncomfortable.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: 1996. Dexter wants to impress his new girlfriend's parents, but the visit doesn't go according to plan. Over dinner, he gets a call from his agent.

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: 1997. The two bump into each other at a university friend's wedding. After an awkward reunion, they get lost in conversation together.

episodes.name: Episode 11
episodes.overview: 1998. Dexter's still adjusting to domestic life. On an evening in, he finds an old mixtape from Emma and calls her to chat about times gone by.

episodes.name: Episode 12
episodes.overview: 1999. A troubled Dexter visits Emma, who's thriving in Paris. As they wander the streets, the memory of their encounter months before hangs in the air.

episodes.name: Episode 13
episodes.overview: 2000. 2001. 2002. Em and Dex's bond grows tighter as the years pass. Her writing's going well, and he starts his own business.
